♪ A GUN AND HOLSTER ♪

48:44.110 --> 48:46.577
♪ SHININ' SILVER SHOOTER ♪

48:46.579 --> 48:50.581
♪ CAUSE HE DON'T
PLAY GAMES ♪

48:50.583 --> 48:53.284
