WELL THEY KNOW ♪

48:59.759 --> 49:03.795
♪ HE AIN'T GOT NO BRAIN ♪

49:03.797 --> 49:07.731
♪ OH, MR. BOLGER STRAP ♪

49:07.733 --> 49:10.300
♪ A GUN AND HOLSTER ♪

49:10.302 --> 49:14.838
♪ SHININ' SILVER SHOOTER ♪

49:14.840 --> 49:16.441
OH, HEY...

49:16.443 --> 49:18.242
WHERE THE HELL
ARE YOU GOING?

49:18.244 --> 49:19.811
