49:19.813 --> 49:24.684
UH-UH, WE, UH... WE HAVE
TO FINISH THIS WHISKEY.

49:28.855 --> 49:30.155
UH-UH.

49:30.157 --> 49:31.688
I CAN'T DRINK THAT.

49:31.690 --> 49:34.291
YEAH, YOU CAN.

49:34.293 --> 49:36.797
I DON'T WANT IT.

49:38.164 --> 49:40.768
AW, JOSEPH,
QUIT BEING A PUSSY.

49:50.809 --> 49:52.846
YOU'RE AN ASSHOLE.

49:56.750 --> 49:59.284
I'M THE ASSHOLE, HMM?

49:59.286 --> 50:00.885
THAT'S RICH.

50:00.887 --> 50:03.588
YOU'RE A STRANGE LITTLE BITCH
NEVER TALKS TO NOBODY.

50:03.590 --> 50:05.490
I NEVER SEEN YOU
WITH A CHICK,

50:05.492 --> 50:07.858
NEVER SEEN YOU
WITH ANYBODY.

50:07.860 --> 50:10.628
YOU'RE JUST LUCKY HOWARD AND I
LET YOU HANG OUT WITH US.

50:10.630 --> 50:12.532
FUCK YOU!

50:18.771 --> 50:21.307
I'M NOTHING.

50:24.878 --> 50:27.314
YOU DONE?

50:38.891 --> 50:41.494
WAS THAT SO BAD, HUH?

50:51.905 --> 50:54.375
[NO AUDIO]

52:48.355 --> 52:50.755
WHERE DID YOU COME FROM?

52:50.757 --> 52:53.360
SAME PLACE YOU GOIN'.

53:22.822 --> 53:25.956
THIS IS ALL A GIFT,

53:25.958 --> 53:29.793
A GUIDE TO YOUR TRUTH,

53:29.795 --> 53:32.398
AS REAL AS THIS HERE
SAND AND SEA.

53:34.032 --> 53:35.402
WHAT IS?

53:38.538 --> 53:40.838
MY STORY.

53:40.840 --> 53:42.643
THE ONE YOU SEEK.

56:20.632 --> 56:22.967
