[GROANING]

56:29.608 --> 56:31.511
I'M FINE.

56:32.679 --> 56:34.882
WHERE'S J?

56:36.081 --> 56:38.048
HUH.

56:38.050 --> 56:39.719
NO IDEA.

56:44.623 --> 56:46.025
HEY, MAN, YOU WANNA
GET OUTTA HERE?

56:48.360 --> 56:49.793
WE NEED SOME WOMEN.

56:49.795 --> 56:52.829
GOOD LUCK.
YOU LOOK LIKE SHIT.

56:52.831 --> 56:54.298
[CHUCKLING]

56:54.300 --> 56:58.071
