THAN AN ASHTRAY.

57:00.873 --> 57:02.909
YEAH, RIGHT.

57:32.639 --> 57:34.307
HEY.

57:36.242 --> 57:37.742
HEY.

57:37.744 --> 57:42.979
♪ SUMMER DAYS WERE JUST
A MAGAZINE ♪

57:42.981 --> 57:46.052
- HOW'S IT GOIN'?
- GOOD.

57:47.887 --> 57:49.086
HOW ARE YOU?

57:49.088 --> 57:52.926
♪ CUTTING GRASS
FOR GASOLINE ♪

57:54.893 --> 57:57.263
I'M FINE.

58:15.782 --> 58:17.380
STAY CLEAR.

58:17.382 --> 58:20.086
SHE SWOONED
FOR THE MOON.

58:23.222 --> 58:25.125
ALWAYS BE HERE.

58:31.230 --> 58:33.367
WHAT WAS THAT?

58:37.402 --> 58:39.739
JUST SOMETHING I WROTE.

58:45.478 --> 58:48.648
"SWOONED FOR THE MOON."

59:01.927 --> 59:03.429
YOU'RE SWEET.

59:35.061 --> 59:38.762
